### Exercise 1-a

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuIyBXaGljaCBmbGlnaHQgb3BlcmF0b3JzIGFyZSBwcmVzZW50P1xuZmxpZ2h0cyAlPiUgZGlzdGluY3QoY2FycmllcikgJT4lIGFycmFuZ2UoZGVzYyhjYXJyaWVyKSlcblxuIyBGaWx0ZXIgVUEsIEFBLCBETFxuZmxpZ2h0cyAlPiUgZmlsdGVyKGNhcnJpZXIgJWluJSBjKFwiVUFcIiwgXCJBQVwiLCBcIkRMXCIpKVxuIyAxMzk1MDQgZmxpZ2h0c1xuYGBgIn0= -->

## Select

### Exercise 1
Different select routes for dep_time, dep_delay, arr_time, and arr_delay from flights.

<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->

```r
# glimpse(flights)
library(microbenchmark)
dplyr1 <- flights %>% select(dep_time, dep_delay, arr_time, arr_delay)
dplyr1_2 <- select(flights, dep_time, dep_delay, arr_time, arr_delay)
dplyr2 <- flights %>% select(starts_with("dep_"),  starts_with("arr_"))
dplyr2_2 <- select(flights, starts_with("dep_"),  starts_with("arr_"))
# Base R
vars <- c("dep_time", "dep_delay", "arr_time", "arr_delay")
base1 <- flights[vars]
# Time
bench <- microbenchmark(dplyr1, dplyr1_2, dplyr2, dplyr2_2, base1, times = 10000L)
bench
```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<!-- rnb-output-begin  -->

<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuc2VsZWN0KGZsaWdodHMsIGNvbnRhaW5zKFwiVElNRVwiLCBpZ25vcmUuY2FzZSA9IEZBTFNFKSlcbmBgYCJ9 -->
